data.description: Sitting on 2 lots, this charming home features 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, wood burning fireplace, updated bathroom, and 2268 square feet of living space.  The original hardwood floors and woodwork show amazing craftsmanship and detail. Plumbing has been recently redone with pex and pvc to the cleanout. Additional updates include a newer metal roof and a privacy fence to enjoy the oversized yard! This property is a unique blend of classic style and modern updates. Call for your showing today.
